snippet.title: Plasma Sky Update 5
snippet.description:
This is update is huge! It ought to be since it took so long to finish!

It’s all free, here’s what you get:
- A revamped Conquest mode with twenty new levels
- New Music
- Full screen on all devices, no more bars
- Five new bosses, double the original number. They’re neat!
- New Blockade levels, full of all new enemies
- Blockade Mode, because Blockade levels are awesome and play really different
- New Power-Up, Laser Meteors, Bullet Physics, Smart Turrets, Visual Enhancements, Bug Fixes!
